  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This retrospective double-cohort study seeks to:

        1. Describe the cardiovascular manifestations and electrophysiological (EP) substrate in
           COVID-19 infection and their association with clinical outcomes; and

        2. Develop a method of cardiovascular risk stratification in COVID-19
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
